{"tid":2222114,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣14名惡漢持錘子及鐵棒　扑爆辦公室玻璃電腦螢幕","createTime":"2020-09-29T01:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T15:22:10.000Z","uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70db6ce61388addec3cbe5c8888ac095e7b51be6","tid":2222114,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"啲員工唔洗返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（29日）凌晨3時許，警方接獲報案指，荃灣楊屋道168號國際訊通中心一個辦公室，被14名男子以錘子及鐵棒毀壞上址23個電腦螢幕、4部電腦主機及7塊玻璃，兇徒其後逃去。警員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列刑事毀壞，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，警方正追緝年該14名約20至30歲涉案男子。"},{"pid":"bf29a220b809e4260670a6af5bcfa2a20bf227a1","tid":2222114,"uid":51592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"係咪員工搞事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0460a2d6c3f4f504c3fa2b454df6c326792a53b4","tid":2222114,"uid":350606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85603b81f8efc51d75541d0916bcf30511df970c","tid":2222114,"uid":5069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:35:01.000Z","msg":"又要內部調查了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4129f4a8a7bcff46eaeab1529eb0963f7d84bc9d","tid":2222114,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093b9fd3c1a991c2a8b56b1feb9b1b0fc6bcc915","tid":2222114,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"員工表示係要返工嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28482de8659ff30bbe270678db9409d1031c8bf","tid":2222114,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"黨衛軍 收唔到保護費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/b